---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const sections = [
  {
    title: 'Choosing a Hosting Provider',
    content: `
      Popular hosting options for Discord bots:
      
      1. **Cloud Platforms**
         - Heroku
         - DigitalOcean
         - AWS
         - Google Cloud
      
      2. **VPS Providers**
         - Linode
         - Vultr
         - OVH
      
      3. **Free Hosting**
         - Oracle Cloud Free Tier
         - Google Cloud Free Tier
         - Railway
    `
  },
  {
    title: 'Deployment Process',
    content: `
      Steps to deploy your bot:

      1. Prepare your code
         - Set up environment variables
         - Install dependencies
         - Configure start script
      
      2. Choose deployment method
         - Git integration
         - Docker containers
         - Manual deployment
      
      3. Set up monitoring
         - Uptime checking
         - Error logging
         - Performance metrics
    `
  },
  {
    title: 'Best Practices',
    content: `
      Follow these deployment best practices:

      1. **Security**
         - Use environment variables
         - Keep tokens secure
         - Regular security updates
      
      2. **Reliability**
         - Implement error handling
         - Set up automatic restarts
         - Use process managers (PM2)
      
      3. **Monitoring**
         - Set up logging
         - Monitor resource usage
         - Configure alerts
    `
  }
];
---

<Layout title="Discord Bot Hosting Guide">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Hosting Your Discord Bot</h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-12">
      {sections.map((section, index) => (
        <div class="bg-[#2B2D31] p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
            <span class="text-[#5865F2] mr-2">{index + 1}.</span>
            {section.title}
          </h2>
          <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
            {section.content}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-between">
      <a 
        href="/bot-development" 
        class="bg-[#4F545C] hover:bg-[#686D73] px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors"
      >
        ← Back to Bot Development
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/docs/deployment/scaling" 
        class="bg-[#5865F2] hover:bg-[#4752C4] px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors"
      >
        Next: Scaling Your Bot →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>